Name: Prehistorik
About the game: Half Human, Half Hungry Raider of the lost Nosh! Prehistorik, a member of the T-Bone Tribe, is hungry and ready for a bronco lunch! Armed with Diner-Club, his faithful frazzler, he sets off on his food-spotting expedition. Follow Prehistorik from the unexplored ice-fields of Antarctica, the darkened mysterious caverns of the shady continent to the lush jungles of the Tropics. Featuring - Rhino Dendron - King-Kongorus XII - Chimp-Agogo - Boa-Dee-Sauce - Pyro-Tax - And many other Chops Lunch is served!
